## CSS Grid Revolution

CSS Grid is a two-dimensional layout system...

### Basic Concepts

```css
.container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: 2rem;
}
```

This single rule creates a fully responsive grid!
